    <item>
      <title>加纳非法淘金热引发的争斗暴露了选举风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-12-04/ghana-election-throws-spotlight-on-illegal-gold-mining</link>
      <description><![CDATA[负债累累的西非国家——将于 12 月 7 日举行选举——可能因非法采金而损失数十亿美元，而非法采金正在造成环境灾难。政府会关闭这个国家吗？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-12-04/ghana-election-throws-spotlight-on-illegal-gold-mining</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 04:00:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>可能接替韩国总统尹永康的领先候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/leading-contenders-who-might-replace-south-korean-president-yoon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈采取戏剧性举措实施戒严，几个小时后又改变主意，这立即引发了人们对这位极不受欢迎的领导人未来的质疑。反对派政客已经要求尹锡烈下台，如果他不下台，他可能会被议会弹劾。总统的任期将持续到 2027 年，但如果他提前离任，将引发选举来决定他的继任者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/leading-contenders-who-might-replace-south-korean-president-yoon</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 03:54:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国戒严混乱的背后原因及其重要性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/what-s-behind-south-korea-s-martial-law-chaos-will-yoon-be-impeached</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是韩国近 40 年前实现完全民主以来，总统首次宣布戒严，引发了一场影响全球的政治危机，并最初导致该国资产价格大幅下跌。该法令在大约六个小时后被撤销，引发了公众的强烈反对，议会罕见地一致投票要求结束戒严。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/what-s-behind-south-korea-s-martial-law-chaos-will-yoon-be-impeached</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 03:48:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国反对党寻求弹劾尹永哲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/south-korea-opposition-party-seeks-to-impeach-yoon-for-treason-m49amyj3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国主要反对党宣布将寻求弹劾总统尹锡烈，因他短暂实施戒严令震惊全国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/south-korea-opposition-party-seeks-to-impeach-yoon-for-treason-m49amyj3</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 02:53:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国人走出戒严混乱，震惊转为愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/as-koreans-emerge-from-martial-law-chaos-shock-turns-to-anger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统尹锡烈试图实施戒严，但未获成功。此举激怒了韩国民众，令这个因长期遭受独裁镇压而伤痕累累的国家陷入混乱。此后，愤怒的韩国民众开始集会反对他。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/as-koreans-emerge-from-martial-law-chaos-shock-turns-to-anger</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 02:50:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾称中国船只向其船只发射水炮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/philippines-says-china-ship-fired-water-cannon-on-its-vessel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾称，一艘中国海警船向其船只发射了水炮，而一艘中国海军舰艇在有争议的南海浅滩附近采取了“危险”行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/philippines-says-china-ship-fired-water-cannon-on-its-vessel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 01:57:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国股市下跌，韩元在尹永康短暂戒严后回升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/korean-won-gains-stocks-dip-after-president-s-brief-martial-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈宣布短暂戒严后，投资者准备迎接长期的政治不确定性，因此，周三韩国货币出现回升，但股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/korean-won-gains-stocks-dip-after-president-s-brief-martial-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 00:04:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国为缓解监狱危机建设项目成本几乎翻倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/costs-almost-double-in-uk-building-program-to-ease-prison-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据支出监督机构称，英国旨在缓解监狱过度拥挤危机的监狱建设计划将延迟五年，且成本几乎是最初预算的两倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/costs-almost-double-in-uk-building-program-to-ease-prison-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普援引拜登赦免令纽约封口费案被驳回</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/trump-says-hush-money-case-must-be-tossed-citing-biden-pardon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的律师告诉法官，由于他在选举中获胜，他因在纽约收取封口费而被定罪的案件必须被撤销，律师辩称，候任总统遭到了检察官的不公平对待。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/trump-says-hush-money-case-must-be-tossed-citing-biden-pardon</guid>
